description: Uses the GitHub API to comment on or close issues.

args: command: (required) Must be either "comment" or "close".
args: repo: (required) The repository to comment on or close an issue in. Must be in the format "owner/repo".
args: number: (required) The issue number to comment on or close.
args: comment: (required if command is "comment") The comment to post on the issue.

#!${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/bin/gptscript-go-tool "${GPTSCRIPT_INPUT}"
